the list of tools to build freefem++ on MacOS are:

Apple's Developer Tools

X11 

To compile ARPACK for eigen value computation 
 we need   fortran  compiler
  see  http://hpc.sourceforge.net/    and get g77 or gfortran 
  or install g77 from fink installer  
  or you can use f2c and fort77 wrapper

latex en pdflatex 
 http://tug.ctan.org/cgi-bin/getFile.py?fn=/systems/mac/mactex/MacTeX-20060314.dmg